<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.3.7">
<l>veñciṉak kaḷiṟum villoṭu mallum vekuṇṭiṟut taṭarttavaṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>kañcaṉaik kāynta kāḷaiyam māṉaik karumukil tiruniṟat tavaṉai</l>
<l>ceñcoṉāṉ maṟaiyōr nāṅkainaṉ ṉaṭuvuḷcempoṉcey kōyili ṉuḷḷē,</l>
<l>yañcaṉak kuṉṟam niṉṟatop pāṉaik kaṇṭukoṇ ṭallaltīrn tēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having seen for myself, within the Cempoṉcey Temple</l>
<l rend="indent">right in the center of Nāṅkai with experts of the four Vedas</l>
<l rend="indent">of elegant words,</l>
<l>The one who raged at, snapped, and destroyed</l>
<l rend="indent">the angry elephant, the bow, and the wrestlers,</l>
<l>The youth who killed Kaṁsa, the lord, the one whose divine hue</l>
<l rend="indent">is of a dark cloud,</l>
<l>The one enduring [like] a dark mountain, I ceased [all] sorrows.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
